➜在软件帮助下检验校园建设
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=15399	32400
BBC英伦网<a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/ukchina/simp/uk_education/2009/12/091217_edu_ukschools.shtml">报道</a>，英国伯明翰的师生可以用“<a href="http://pressitt.com/smnr/new-interactive-online-3d-tool-enables-teachers-students-and-planners-to-test-learning-environments/705/">学习环境虚拟现实网络模拟器</a>”（The Learning Environment Virtual Reality Online Simulator, LEVROS）来了解和检验学校的硬件设施以及修缮计划。<i>
